</div></div></section></section><section id="REF-JOI240124" class="ref-list"><h2 class="pmc_sec_title">References</h2>
<section id="REF-JOI240124_sec2"><ul class="ref-list font-sm" style="list-style-type:none">
<li id="joi240124r1">
<span class="label">1.</span><cite>Stafie CS, Sufaru IG, Ghiciuc CM, et al. Exploring the intersection of artificial intelligence and clinical healthcare: a multidisciplinary review. Diagnostics (Basel). 2023;13(12):1995. doi: 10.3390/diagnostics13121995

